{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rsv:ezra.2",
    "translationId": "rsv",
    "bookSlug": "ezra",
    "chapterNumber": 2,
    "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2",
    "summary": "Source text for Ezra 2 in Revised Standard Version."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:1",
      "text": "Now these were the people of the province who came up out of the captivity of those exiles whom Nebuchadnezzar the king of Babylon had carried captive to Babylonia; they returned to Jerusalem and Judah, each to his own town.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:2",
      "text": "They came with Zerubbabel, Jeshua, Nehemiah, Seraiah, Reel-aiah, Mordecai, Bilshan, Mispar, Bigvai, Rehum, and Baanah. The number of the men of the people of Israel:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:3",
      "text": "the sons of Parosh, two thousand one hundred and seventy-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:4",
      "text": "The sons of Shephatiah, three hundred and seventy-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:5",
      "text": "The sons of Arah, seven hundred and seventy-five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:6",
      "text": "The sons of Pahath-moab, namely the sons of Jeshua and Joab, two thousand eight hundred and twelve.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:7",
      "text": "The sons of Elam, one thousand two hundred and fifty-four.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:8",
      "text": "The sons of Zattu, nine hundred and forty-five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:9",
      "text": "The sons of Zaccai, seven hundred and sixty.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:10",
      "text": "The sons of Bani, six hundred and forty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.11",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:11",
      "text": "The sons of Bebai, six hundred and twenty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.12",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:12",
      "text": "The sons of Azgad, one thousand two hundred and twenty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.13",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:13",
      "text": "The sons of Adonikam, six hundred and sixty-six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.14",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:14",
      "text": "The sons of Bigvai, two thousand and fifty-six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.15",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:15",
      "text": "The sons of Adin, four hundred and fifty-four.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.16",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:16",
      "text": "The sons of Ater, namely of Hezekiah, ninety-eight.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.17",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:17",
      "text": "The sons of Bezai, three hundred and twenty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.18",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:18",
      "text": "The sons of Jorah, one hundred and twelve.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.19",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:19",
      "text": "The sons of Hashum, two hundred and twenty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.20",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:20",
      "text": "The sons of Gibbar, ninety-five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.21",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:21",
      "text": "The sons of Bethlehem, one hundred and twenty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.22",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:22",
      "text": "The men of Netophah, fifty-six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.23",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:23",
      "text": "The men of Anathoth, one hundred and twenty-eight.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.24",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:24",
      "text": "The sons of Azmaveth, forty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.25",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:25",
      "text": "The sons of Kiriatharim, Chephirah, and Be-eroth, seven hundred and forty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.26",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:26",
      "text": "The sons of Ramah and Geba, six hundred and twenty-one.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.27",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:27",
      "text": "The men of Michmas, one hundred and twenty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.28",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:28",
      "text": "The men of Bethel and Ai, two hundred and twenty-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.29",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:29",
      "text": "The sons of Nebo, fifty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.30",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:30",
      "text": "The sons of Magbish, one hundred and fifty-six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.31",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:31",
      "text": "The sons of the other Elam, one thousand two hundred and fifty-four.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.32",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:32",
      "text": "The sons of Harim, three hundred and twenty.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.33",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:33",
      "text": "The sons of Lod, Hadid, and Ono, seven hundred and twenty-five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.34",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:34",
      "text": "The sons of Jericho, three hundred and forty-five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.35",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:35",
      "text": "The sons of Senaah, three thousand six hundred and thirty.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.36",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:36",
      "text": "The priests: the sons of Jedaiah, of the house of Jeshua, nine hundred and seventy-three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.37",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:37",
      "text": "The sons of Immer, one thousand and fifty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.38",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:38",
      "text": "The sons of Pashhur, one thousand two hundred and forty-seven.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.39",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:39",
      "text": "The sons of Harim, one thousand and seventeen.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.40",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:40",
      "text": "The Levites: the sons of Jeshua and Kadmi-el, of the sons of Hodaviah, seventy-four.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.41",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:41",
      "text": "The singers: the sons of Asaph, one hundred and twenty-eight.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.42",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:42",
      "text": "The sons of the gatekeepers: the sons of Shallum, the sons of Ater, the sons of Talmon, the sons of Akkub, the sons of Hatita, and the sons of Shobai, in all one hundred and thirty-nine.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.43",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:43",
      "text": "The temple servants: the sons of Ziha, the sons of Hasupha, the sons of Tabbaoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.44",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:44",
      "text": "the sons of Keros, the sons of Siaha, the sons of Padon,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.45",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:45",
      "text": "the sons of Lebanah, the sons of Hagabah, the sons of Akkub,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.46",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:46",
      "text": "the sons of Hagab, the sons of Shamlai, the sons of Hanan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.47",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:47",
      "text": "the sons of Giddel, the sons of Gahar, the sons of Re-aiah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.48",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:48",
      "text": "the sons of Rezin, the sons of Nekoda, the sons of Gazzam,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.49",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:49",
      "text": "the sons of Uzza, the sons of Paseah, the sons of Besai,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.50",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:50",
      "text": "the sons of Asnah, the sons of Me-unim, the sons of Nephisim,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.51",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:51",
      "text": "the sons of Bakbuk, the sons of Hakupha, the sons of Harhur,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.52",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:52",
      "text": "the sons of Bazluth, the sons of Mehida, the sons of Harsha,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.53",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:53",
      "text": "the sons of Barkos, the sons of Sisera, the sons of Temah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.54",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:54",
      "text": "the sons of Neziah, and the sons of Hatipha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.55",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:55",
      "text": "The sons of Solomon's servants: the sons of Sotai, the sons of Hassophereth, the sons of Peruda,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.56",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:56",
      "text": "the sons of Jaalah, the sons of Darkon, the sons of Giddel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.57",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 57,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:57",
      "text": "the sons of Shephatiah, the sons of Hattil, the sons of Pochereth-hazzebaim, and the sons of Ami.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.58",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 58,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:58",
      "text": "All the temple servants and the sons of Solomon's servants were three hundred and ninety-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.59",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 59,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:59",
      "text": "The following were those who came up from Tel-melah, Tel-harsha, Cherub, Addan, and Immer, though they could not prove their fathers' houses or their descent, whether they belonged to Israel:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.60",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 60,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:60",
      "text": "the sons of Delaiah, the sons of Tobiah, and the sons of Nekoda, six hundred and fifty-two.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.61",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 61,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:61",
      "text": "Also, of the sons of the priests: the sons of Habaiah, the sons of Hakkoz, and the sons of Barzillai (who had taken a wife from the daughters of Barzillai the Gileadite, and was called by their name).",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.62",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 62,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:62",
      "text": "These sought their registration among those enrolled in the genealogies, but they were not found there, and so they were excluded from the priesthood as unclean;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.63",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 63,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:63",
      "text": "the governor told them that they were not to partake of the most holy food, until there should be a priest to consult Urim and Thummim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.64",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 64,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:64",
      "text": "The whole assembly together was forty-two thousand three hundred and sixty,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.65",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 65,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:65",
      "text": "besides their menservants and maidservants, of whom there were seven thousand three hundred and thirty-seven; and they had two hundred male and female singers.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.66",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 66,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:66",
      "text": "Their horses were seven hundred and thirty-six, their mules were two hundred and forty-five,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.67",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 67,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:67",
      "text": "their camels were four hundred and thirty-five, and their asses were six thousand seven hundred and twenty.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.68",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 68,
      "referenceLabel": "Ezra 2:68",
      "text": "Some of the heads of families, when they came to the house of the Lord which is in Jerusalem, made freewill offerings for the house of God, to erect it on its site;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:ezra.2.69",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "ezra",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
